    "summary": "Lufthansa exposes two REST/OpenAPI surfaces for developers: a public Open API and a partner API, both on https://api.lufthansa.com/v1 and documented on developer.lufthansa.com, using OAuth2 bearer tokens obtained from developer-issued application credentials.",
